Summary: Look like a star looked far away. and move away from where I was standing
divs: Sighting DetailsI went outside to smoke, I looked up at the stars, and I could see what I thought, looked just like a star, moving slowly north west. The object had no flashing or blinking lights .For the amount of time I watched the object, It had to have been moving fast to travel as far as it did. I cant estimate the speed. but the object was too big just disappear. The size of the object did not change as it traveled. When I discovered the object, I did not know if it was moving or not.
